        <mxCell id="24" value="Worker Node 1" style="swimlane;startSize=35;fillColor=#E3EFFC;strokeColor=#1A66B5;fontColor=#0C3F75;fontStyle=1;fontSize=12;fontFamily=Arial;strokeWidth=2;rounded=1;arcSize=2;" vertex="1" parent="19">
          <mxGeometry x="15" y="210" width="1565" height="310" as="geometry"/>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="25" value="🛡️ C-VEN
(Container Virtual Enforcement Node)

DaemonSet — one per worker node
Enforcement agent on host
Owns ILLUMIO_* iptables chains
Heartbeats to PCE every ~5 minutes" style="rounded=1;arcSize=5;fillColor=#E3EFFC;strokeColor=#1A66B5;fontColor=#0C3F75;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Arial;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeWidth=1.5;" vertex="1" parent="24">
          <mxGeometry x="15" y="40" width="310" height="155" as="geometry"/>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="26" value="💾 Storage Pod

DaemonSet — one per worker node
Local policy cache (embedded etcd)
Buffers flow telemetry before upload
Serves compiled policy to C-VEN
Provides CLAS local store" style="rounded=1;arcSize=5;fillColor=#FEF0DA;strokeColor=#9B5E0C;fontColor=#6B3D06;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Arial;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeWidth=1.5;" vertex="1" parent="24">
