        <mxCell id="38" value="LEGEND
━━ Purple dashed → Policy push (PCE to CLAS to Storage Pod to C-VEN to iptables)
━━ Teal dashed   → Kubelink sync (Kubernetes API to PCE workload inventory)
━━ Amber dashed  → Telemetry upload (pod flows to Storage Pod to PCE to Splunk)
━━ Blue solid    → C-VEN heartbeat (to PCE API port 443 every ~5 minutes)" style="rounded=1;arcSize=3;fillColor=#F5F2EC;strokeColor=#6B6860;fontColor=#3F3E3A;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Arial;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;spacingLeft=8;strokeWidth=1;" vertex="1" parent="1">
