Logged as Unknown.
Visible in Explorer
as Potentially Blocked." style="rounded=1;arcSize=5;fillColor=#FEF0DA;strokeColor=#9B5E0C;fontColor=#6B3D06;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Arial;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeWidth=1.5;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="800" y="640" width="220" height="160" as="geometry"/>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="36" value="Idle / Visibility" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;strokeWidth=2.5;strokeColor=#9B5E0C;endArrow=block;endFill=1;fontFamily=Arial;fontSize=10;fontColor=#9B5E0C;fontStyle=1;rounded=1;" edge="1" source="31" target="35" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"/>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="37" value="📊 Flow Record Captured

C-VEN records: src IP, dst IP, port, protocol, pd decision
Storage Pod buffers the record locally
Uploads to PCE Event Service on schedule
PCE forwards to Splunk via syslog
Visible in PCE Explorer and Splunk dashboards" style="rounded=1;arcSize=3;fillColor=#EDE9FD;strokeColor=#5B4CC4;fontColor=#3B2E8A;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Arial;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;spacingLeft=8;strokeWidth=1;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="480" y="870" width="560" height="130" as="geometry"/>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="38" value="🛡️ CLAS Resilience

CLAS mode: policy served from local cluster cache
PCE outage does NOT interrupt enforcement
C-VEN continues enforcing cached rules indefinitely

Legacy mode: C-VEN contacts PCE directly
PCE 406 throttling = policy update failures
PCE outage = degraded mode (last known policy held)" style="rounded=1;arcSize=3;fillColor=#E0F5EC;strokeColor=#0D7A5F;fontColor=#064F3C;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Arial;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;spacingLeft=8;strokeWidth=1;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="480" y="1030" width="560" height="155" as="geometry"/>
        </mxCell>

      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
